WEBVTT

01:37.100 --> 01:41.030
[The Best Thing]

01:41.350 --> 01:45.620
[Episode 3: Licorice root, with its sweet flavor and neutral nature, is renowned for tonifying the spleen, boosting qi, clearing heat and toxins, dispelling phlegm, relieving coughs, alleviating acute pain, and harmonizing the effects of other medicinal agents.]

01:46.789 --> 01:48.310
The guests attending the JIC Summit

01:46.810 --> 01:53.060
[The first day of the JIC Summit in Hang City]

01:48.310 --> 01:48.870
will be here soon.

01:49.120 --> 01:50.650
All departments must gather the strength

01:50.680 --> 01:52.680
and take this reception work seriously.

01:52.700 --> 01:53.400
-Got it.
-Got it.

01:59.979 --> 02:01.140
Is the ninth floor okay?

02:01.340 --> 02:01.940
Yes, that's fine.

02:01.940 --> 02:03.730
Hello, sir. Please take your room card and ID card.

02:03.730 --> 02:04.530
This way, please.

02:06.420 --> 02:06.980
Hello.

02:07.250 --> 02:08.180
Manager Shen,

02:08.410 --> 02:08.900
can you hear me?

02:09.090 --> 02:09.900
Yes.

02:09.900 --> 02:11.130
A guest doesn't want to stay in a villa.

02:11.130 --> 02:12.460
Can you arrange another room?

02:13.970 --> 02:17.500
Take him to the Presidential Suite 1807.

02:17.500 --> 02:18.970
Then ask someone to help with his luggage.

02:19.130 --> 02:19.690
Okay.

02:21.020 --> 02:21.650
Hello.

02:25.220 --> 02:27.220
Based on the X-ray images,

02:27.550 --> 02:29.020
the patient's lung tissue in this area

02:29.090 --> 02:30.620
has already developed some fibrosis.

02:31.630 --> 02:33.700
At this stage of radiation pneumonitis,

02:33.810 --> 02:34.900
promoting blood circulation and resolving phlegm

02:34.920 --> 02:36.480
are more critical than clearing heat and relieving coughs.

02:37.530 --> 02:38.780
By improving blood circulation and resolving phlegm,

02:38.780 --> 02:41.370
we can enhance the pulmonary blood flow,

02:41.690 --> 02:43.360
thereby improving lung function

02:43.570 --> 02:45.079
and reducing the risk of infection.

02:59.060 --> 02:59.780
What's the matter?

03:06.870 --> 03:07.670
Fine.

03:10.310 --> 03:11.150
Head Nurse.

03:12.300 --> 03:13.010
Perfect timing.

03:13.300 --> 03:14.220
Please sign this.

03:14.220 --> 03:14.780
Okay.

03:15.430 --> 03:17.160
Let's go see a movie tonight.

03:17.440 --> 03:18.530
What movie?

03:19.360 --> 03:22.190
This one. It's a new tearjerker.

03:22.220 --> 03:23.690
I heard it's really touching.

03:24.130 --> 03:25.020
I'd feel a bit awkward

03:25.020 --> 03:25.740
going alone as a man.

03:25.740 --> 03:26.740
Let's go together.

03:27.960 --> 03:29.000
Just the two of us?

03:29.680 --> 03:30.840
Senior He is busy.

03:35.780 --> 03:36.220
The pen.

03:46.130 --> 03:47.650
The week-long JIC Summit will

03:47.650 --> 03:49.570
officially begin this Wednesday.

03:52.570 --> 03:53.970
I'm currently

03:53.970 --> 03:55.810
at Gunan Huating Hotel,

03:56.130 --> 03:58.250
where all the guests will be staying.

03:58.530 --> 04:00.500
And this Wednesday, they will...

04:25.790 --> 04:27.140
Everyone, thank you for your hard work yesterday.

04:27.390 --> 04:29.630
Today, we'll have more VIP members checking in.

04:29.940 --> 04:32.330
Also, there'll be a cocktail party for Zhongyu Tech tomorrow evening.

04:32.820 --> 04:33.620
Oh, right.

04:34.010 --> 04:36.010
Zhongyu Tech's executives will arrive this afternoon.

04:36.250 --> 04:38.130
The Front Office must ensure a seamless reception.

04:39.220 --> 04:40.020
Manager Shen?

04:40.790 --> 04:41.560
Manager Shen.

04:44.460 --> 04:47.260
I'll reconfirm the guest list before noon.

04:49.180 --> 04:49.909
Manager Xu,

04:49.930 --> 04:51.840
have you checked the food and beverage stock?

04:52.330 --> 04:53.940
Yes, we're fully stocked.

04:54.690 --> 04:55.570
Thank you all for your hard work.

05:15.540 --> 05:16.660
You two already know?

05:20.180 --> 05:21.940
Do you want to have some days off to rest?

05:21.960 --> 05:23.080
I can cover for you for a couple of days.

05:25.010 --> 05:25.690
No need.

05:27.180 --> 05:27.570
Right,

05:27.570 --> 05:28.980
isn't today Saturday?

05:28.980 --> 05:30.540
Shouldn't you go for your follow-up visit?

05:30.540 --> 05:31.420
Yes.

05:33.370 --> 05:34.050
I forgot.

05:34.570 --> 05:35.690
Then ask for a sick leave now.

05:35.690 --> 05:37.060
Go see your TCM physician and then come back.

05:37.060 --> 05:37.860
I'll keep an eye on things for you.

05:40.060 --> 05:42.740
I'd better not. Didn't General Manager say

05:42.740 --> 05:44.659
we can't leave without permission?

05:44.850 --> 05:46.020
I'll finish my work first

05:46.330 --> 05:47.330
and I'll see about it later.

05:47.890 --> 05:48.540
Okay.

05:55.520 --> 05:58.520
[Honganmen Clinic]

05:56.810 --> 05:57.940
This is your prescription.

05:58.300 --> 05:59.100
Thank you, doctor.

05:59.130 --> 05:59.980
See you next week.

05:59.980 --> 06:00.540
Okay.

06:21.160 --> 06:22.040
She didn't come again?

06:46.180 --> 06:48.010
A heart's ailment demands

06:48.340 --> 06:49.490
a heart's remedy.

06:51.030 --> 06:53.060
Either clear the blockage,

06:53.940 --> 06:54.450
or

06:54.980 --> 06:55.940
uproot the cause.

07:44.980 --> 07:45.980
Sun.

07:46.330 --> 07:47.250
Help me check

07:47.250 --> 07:49.810
if there is an appointment made by Shen Xifan.

07:49.810 --> 07:50.740
Shen Xifan?

07:51.210 --> 07:51.690
Just a moment.

07:55.990 --> 07:57.700
No, she doesn't have an appointment today.

07:59.330 --> 07:59.860
Thank you.

07:59.860 --> 08:00.370
No problem.

08:04.800 --> 08:05.600
Sun.

08:06.250 --> 08:07.180
Give me

08:07.180 --> 08:08.540
Shen Xifan's registered phone number.

08:09.970 --> 08:11.240
Why do you want her phone number?

08:11.520 --> 08:12.670
She didn't come for her follow-up visit today.

08:12.700 --> 08:14.030
I should check on her

08:14.290 --> 08:16.090
and see if she got held up by something.

08:19.670 --> 08:20.820
She's quite young.

08:21.330 --> 08:22.450
Young people nowadays

08:22.450 --> 08:23.180
lack the patience

08:23.180 --> 08:24.010
for TCM remedies.

08:24.010 --> 08:25.890
It's normal for them to bail without warning.

08:26.770 --> 08:28.010
She made an appointment with me last week.

08:29.770 --> 08:31.060
Really?

08:31.060 --> 08:31.660
Okay.

08:32.179 --> 08:32.940
Just a moment.

08:34.539 --> 08:35.299
One...

08:43.350 --> 08:43.840
Here.

08:45.470 --> 08:46.470
You owe me a meal.

08:47.390 --> 08:48.510
I owe you a meal?

08:49.090 --> 08:50.490
This is about being responsible for the patient.

08:51.020 --> 08:51.690
Responsible.

08:51.690 --> 08:52.660
Put on your mask.

08:55.780 --> 08:56.660
Ms. Fang,

08:56.660 --> 08:57.570
we knew you were coming.

08:57.570 --> 08:59.900
We've already placed your favorite aromatherapy in your room.

09:00.450 --> 09:01.540
Your room card will be ready in a moment.

09:01.590 --> 09:02.380
Okay, thank you.

09:07.300 --> 09:07.970
Mr. Yan!

09:10.490 --> 09:11.300
Ms. Fang.

09:13.490 --> 09:14.970
Long time no see.

09:14.970 --> 09:15.780
Long time no see.

09:17.180 --> 09:17.610
Shen.

09:18.060 --> 09:19.940
Please handle Mr. Yan's check-in as well.

09:20.140 --> 09:21.180
Sure, no problem.

09:21.470 --> 09:23.540
Mr. Yan, this is Shen.

09:23.900 --> 09:25.850
She's the manager of this hotel's Front Office Department.

09:26.540 --> 09:28.690
If there's anything you need during your stay,

09:28.690 --> 09:29.850
you can ask her for help.

09:37.210 --> 09:38.570
You came alone today?

09:38.570 --> 09:40.140
Your two sons didn't come with you?

09:40.850 --> 09:41.830
My eldest son...

09:41.870 --> 09:42.910
He is busy

09:42.940 --> 09:45.140
managing some issues at his company's branch.

09:45.380 --> 09:46.540
My younger son, Yan Heng,

09:46.540 --> 09:48.900
is busy with his small robotics company.

09:49.230 --> 09:51.110
He's not qualified, so I didn't let him come.

09:51.540 --> 09:52.690
Robotics, right?

09:54.140 --> 09:55.780
What a coincidence. I have a niece

09:55.780 --> 09:58.420
who pays much attention to the AI industry.

09:58.660 --> 10:00.850
These two kids should meet.

10:00.850 --> 10:02.420
Sure, why not?

10:02.420 --> 10:03.730
Sounds like they'd have a lot to talk about.

10:03.730 --> 10:05.660
Definitely.

10:05.660 --> 10:06.380
You should arrange it.

10:06.380 --> 10:07.060
Should we arrange it?

10:07.060 --> 10:07.690
Set up a meeting.

10:07.690 --> 10:08.970
How about setting up a meeting for them

10:09.140 --> 10:09.810
and let's have a meal together?

10:09.810 --> 10:10.610
Okay.

10:10.610 --> 10:11.610
That's great.

10:11.610 --> 10:12.900
I agree.

10:13.210 --> 10:14.440
It's settled then.

10:31.690 --> 10:32.730
Hello.

10:33.180 --> 10:33.940
Excuse me,

10:34.300 --> 10:35.610
is this Ms. Shen Xifan?

10:36.300 --> 10:37.180
Yes.

10:37.520 --> 10:38.520
Who am I speaking with?

10:38.780 --> 10:39.730
This is He Suye.

10:41.140 --> 10:42.180
Dr. He.

10:42.420 --> 10:42.940
Hello.

10:45.240 --> 10:46.810
Are you coming today?

10:47.540 --> 10:48.570
I've been waiting for you.

10:52.240 --> 10:53.360
Manager Shen.

10:53.390 --> 10:54.330
Please wait a moment.

10:55.340 --> 10:55.850
Please tell the colleagues

10:55.850 --> 10:57.330
from the Food & Beverage Department

10:57.330 --> 10:59.450
to check when Ms. Fang will finish her afternoon tea.

10:59.800 --> 11:00.970
Make sure to prepare hot water

11:00.990 --> 11:01.810
for her bath later.

11:01.810 --> 11:02.260
Okay.

11:02.330 --> 11:03.180
Thank you.

11:04.900 --> 11:06.140
I'm sorry, Dr. He.

11:06.330 --> 11:07.300
I just had something to attend to.

11:08.430 --> 11:09.840
I just want to ask

11:09.870 --> 11:11.150
how you've been lately.

11:11.170 --> 11:12.930
You didn't come for your follow-up visit today.

11:15.060 --> 11:16.570
I've been a bit too busy lately.

11:16.570 --> 11:18.420
So I didn't have time to go today.

11:20.570 --> 11:21.260
Okay.

11:27.620 --> 11:28.420
Then...

11:28.940 --> 11:29.990
will you come next week?

11:31.040 --> 11:31.710
Of course,

11:31.740 --> 11:33.110
I'll be there next week.

11:34.150 --> 11:41.680
♫So I wait and wander, but the outcome isn't so bad♫

11:36.460 --> 11:38.060
How have you been feeling lately?

11:38.490 --> 11:40.490
Have your symptoms of trouble sleeping, chest tightness, and anxiety

11:40.660 --> 11:41.660
gotten any better?

11:41.730 --> 11:49.140
♫Sparrows gather on the windowsill, sunlight streaming through♫

11:45.810 --> 11:47.180
I've been doing pretty well lately.

11:48.180 --> 11:51.210
At least I'm getting about five hours of sleep now.

11:49.440 --> 11:57.180
♫Poets keep altering words to record the fast-changing world♫

11:51.210 --> 11:52.900
And falling asleep is much easier than before.

11:54.330 --> 11:55.060
That's good.

11:55.810 --> 11:57.540
No matter how busy work gets, you still need to rest.

11:57.380 --> 12:04.580
♫A relationship or an accident♫

11:58.570 --> 11:59.570
If you have time,

11:59.570 --> 12:01.540
try visiting places with lots of trees.

12:05.070 --> 12:08.670
♫It became brighter because of you♫

12:07.380 --> 12:09.090
Places with lots of trees?

12:08.780 --> 12:12.730
♫The world suddenly became so cute♫

12:09.810 --> 12:11.900
That sounds a bit mystical.

12:12.760 --> 12:16.470
♫Maybe I'm too slow to understand♫

12:13.330 --> 12:14.490
Places with lots of trees

12:14.490 --> 12:15.610
have plenty of oxygen,

12:15.610 --> 12:17.420
which can help you relax.

12:16.500 --> 12:20.230
♫I can't confess my passionate love to you♫

12:17.540 --> 12:18.620
Does that sound more scientific?

12:19.390 --> 12:21.440
Much more scientific.

12:20.420 --> 12:24.230
♫Love is an admiration for beauty♫

12:24.260 --> 12:28.150
♫I've decided to only love you♫

12:25.790 --> 12:27.450
Have you run out of your medicine?

12:27.540 --> 12:28.900
Do you need me to prescribe more for you?

12:28.180 --> 12:30.180
♫My foolishness♫

12:29.530 --> 12:32.220
I think I still have a couple of bags left.

12:30.200 --> 12:32.040
♫My sincerity♫

12:32.070 --> 12:34.070
♫Only for one person♫

12:33.180 --> 12:35.490
But I've been really busy lately,

12:35.490 --> 12:36.660
and I get off work late,

12:36.660 --> 12:38.450
so I might not be able to come for a follow-up visit.

12:37.100 --> 12:42.640
♫Because of you, everything brightens up♫

12:40.530 --> 12:41.460
It's okay.

12:41.790 --> 12:44.080
How about this? I'll use last week's prescription

12:44.110 --> 12:45.660
and have the pharmacy decoct it for you.

12:45.870 --> 12:48.160
You can have your family come pick it up.

12:48.720 --> 12:50.560
Sure, no problem.

12:52.380 --> 12:54.970
Can I add you on WeChat through this phone number?

12:55.690 --> 12:57.450
I need to send you a photo of the prescription

12:57.610 --> 12:59.380
so your family can show it when picking up the medicine.

12:59.750 --> 13:00.840
Yes.

13:00.870 --> 13:02.300
This number is my WeChat ID.

13:02.330 --> 13:03.540
You can add me directly.

13:05.210 --> 13:05.950
Okay.

13:06.740 --> 13:08.220
Remember to come for your follow-up visit next week.

13:08.650 --> 13:10.410
I will come next week.

13:10.900 --> 13:11.610
Thank you.

13:11.830 --> 13:12.310
Okay.

13:12.960 --> 13:13.560
Bye bye.

13:15.190 --> 13:15.950
Bye bye.

13:37.240 --> 13:39.820
♫A gentle breeze begins to rise♫

13:41.100 --> 13:45.650
♫You'll see a rainbow♫

13:45.670 --> 13:47.880
♫Hovering in mid-air♫

13:48.990 --> 13:51.600
♫This sweet dream♫

13:53.600 --> 13:58.600
♫All our days are filled with♫

13:58.620 --> 14:02.210
♫Lololove and sunshine♫

14:02.660 --> 14:10.550
♫Close your eyes, and love will never fade away♫

14:10.660 --> 14:18.090
♫Love love love love, is right in front of me♫

14:18.770 --> 14:26.460
♫Ooh love, ooh love, I've seen your face♫

14:27.020 --> 14:34.280
♫Love love love love, is talking right at me♫

14:32.030 --> 14:32.950
Hello, Dr. He.

14:32.970 --> 14:34.120
I'm Shen Xifan.

14:34.590 --> 14:41.530
♫Loving you, loving you, is the best thing I'll ever do♫

14:36.100 --> 14:36.700
Hello.

14:37.490 --> 14:39.060
I'm He Suye.

14:39.350 --> 14:40.740
Please save my contact information.

14:45.420 --> 14:46.420
Thank you.

14:58.760 --> 15:03.630
♫All our days are filled with♫

15:03.650 --> 15:07.210
♫Lololove and sunshine♫

15:07.890 --> 15:15.530
♫Close your eyes, and love will never fade away♫

15:11.820 --> 15:12.540
The photo has been received.

15:15.490 --> 15:17.690
I added licorice root for you.

15:15.810 --> 15:19.020
♫Love love love love♫

15:52.060 --> 15:54.250
Ms. Wu, help decoct this.

15:54.270 --> 15:55.880
The patient's family will come to pick it up later.

15:56.130 --> 15:56.890
Okay.

15:58.940 --> 15:59.780
Wait.

15:59.990 --> 16:02.740
Well... help me pack one more thing separately.

16:27.740 --> 16:29.710
Licorice root, with its sweet flavor and neutral nature,

16:29.730 --> 16:32.230
is renowned for tonifying the spleen, boosting qi, and clearing heat and toxins.

16:32.250 --> 16:34.490
You can steep a few slices in water to drink.

16:34.520 --> 16:36.090
The taste shouldn't lose to bubble tea.

16:37.130 --> 16:37.850
Thank you.

17:02.250 --> 17:03.720
The doctor told you to steep it in water?

17:05.579 --> 17:06.490
That's quite thoughtful.

17:09.730 --> 17:11.210
Drink this first.

17:12.150 --> 17:13.180
Drink it while it's hot.

17:13.210 --> 17:14.180
Don't let it get cold.

17:35.190 --> 17:36.790
It's not bitter.

18:23.110 --> 18:25.280
What made you think of steeping licorice root?

18:25.870 --> 18:27.620
I happened to see some in the kitchen.

18:27.690 --> 18:29.100
so I made two cups.

18:30.010 --> 18:30.730
Not bad.

18:33.410 --> 18:34.540
It clears heat and toxins.

18:33.780 --> 18:36.960
[Licorice root, with its sweet flavor and neutral nature, is renowned for tonifying the spleen, boosting qi, and clearing heat and toxins. It can be steeped in water.]

18:35.250 --> 18:36.620
This season is the right time for drinking it.

18:37.660 --> 18:40.450
Did Shen Xifan you mentioned last time

18:40.770 --> 18:42.340
come for her follow-up visit this week?

18:43.400 --> 18:44.250
No.

18:46.520 --> 18:49.630
You only get to see her once a week when she comes for her follow-up visit.

18:50.180 --> 18:51.490
You've missed this one.

18:51.510 --> 18:54.180
Do you think she might stop coming to the clinic for treatment?

18:51.900 --> 18:55.760
[Licorice root, with its sweet flavor and neutral nature, is renowned for tonifying the spleen, boosting qi, and clearing heat and toxins. It can be steeped in water.]

18:55.780 --> 18:57.500
She won't. She's busy this week.

18:57.530 --> 18:58.770
She'll come for her follow-up visit next week.

19:00.730 --> 19:01.450
Next week?

19:03.950 --> 19:05.190
How do you know that?

19:07.010 --> 19:07.940
I called and asked.

19:08.530 --> 19:09.920
You have her number now?

19:11.910 --> 19:14.630
I got her number from the clinic's registration form.

19:16.180 --> 19:19.030
Didn't you say it's not good to mix personal matters with work?

19:19.050 --> 19:21.600
But you said it's fine to get information

19:21.630 --> 19:22.630
from the registration form, right?

19:25.220 --> 19:26.650
Did you check up on her?

19:27.480 --> 19:28.950
She has a boyfriend.

19:29.420 --> 19:30.900
She has a boyfriend?

19:33.120 --> 19:33.600
Well...

19:35.270 --> 19:38.700
Of course. Such a beautiful and elegant girl

19:40.420 --> 19:42.790
must have many pursuers.

19:45.580 --> 19:46.620
Since that's the case,

19:47.320 --> 19:49.760
you should stop entertaining any thoughts.

19:51.010 --> 19:52.210
As TCM physicians,

19:52.210 --> 19:54.690
we should focus on cultivating our character and maintaining our integrity.

19:56.570 --> 19:58.570
Don't let any messy situations

19:58.600 --> 20:00.120
ruin our reputation.

20:00.720 --> 20:03.190
What else can I say?

20:05.770 --> 20:07.660
Don't worry, I won't do anything reckless.

20:09.110 --> 20:10.550
She has a boyfriend?

20:12.270 --> 20:13.660
What a pity.

20:26.850 --> 20:34.490
[The second day of the JIC Summit in Hang City]

20:28.320 --> 20:29.840
It's the second day of the summit today.

20:29.940 --> 20:31.940
Everyone, ensure our new guests are well taken care of.

20:32.150 --> 20:34.350
Also, for Zhongyu Tech's cocktail party tonight,

20:34.380 --> 20:35.660
make sure everything runs smoothly.

20:35.660 --> 20:36.530
No mistakes.

20:36.530 --> 20:37.420
-Got it.
-Got it.

20:44.010 --> 20:45.250
Cheers.

20:45.700 --> 20:47.350
You gave a great speech today

20:47.380 --> 20:49.380
on stage. You're a young talent.

20:49.480 --> 20:50.190
Mr. Li.

20:50.800 --> 20:52.040
I'll take my leave first.

20:52.060 --> 20:52.650
Okay.

20:52.870 --> 20:54.980
Enjoy the food and drinks and have fun.

20:55.210 --> 20:57.050
-See you.
-Okay.

21:03.920 --> 21:04.680
Let's talk privately.

21:04.730 --> 21:05.820
Don't let what we discuss today be forgotten tomorrow.

21:05.820 --> 21:06.820
How should I put it?

21:06.820 --> 21:08.860
I'm not quite good at drinking.

21:08.860 --> 21:09.580
Once I start, I drink too much.

21:09.580 --> 21:11.660
That's not true. You look quite sober.

21:12.050 --> 21:13.680
It's not appropriate to leave early.

21:15.790 --> 21:16.620
Manager Shen,

21:17.380 --> 21:18.290
please

21:18.730 --> 21:19.940
walk me to the parking lot.

21:22.600 --> 21:24.400
Mr. Yan, let me walk you there.

21:27.150 --> 21:30.000
Perfect. You take my assistant to my room

21:30.030 --> 21:31.550
and bring my luggage to the parking lot.

21:31.810 --> 21:32.320
Thank you.

21:37.660 --> 21:38.140
Okay.

21:39.770 --> 21:40.580
Manager Shen,

21:41.490 --> 21:42.380
thank you.

21:45.340 --> 21:46.420
Okay, no problem.

21:46.440 --> 21:47.290
I'll walk you there.

21:49.050 --> 21:50.340
Then goodbye, Mr. Yan.

21:50.340 --> 21:51.010
Goodbye.

21:51.420 --> 21:52.340
Take care.

21:52.340 --> 21:52.860
Keep in touch.

21:52.860 --> 21:53.620
Keep in touch.

21:53.620 --> 21:54.010
Bye bye.

21:54.010 --> 21:54.730
This way, please.

21:54.730 --> 21:55.210
Okay.

21:55.450 --> 21:56.180
Let's go.

22:04.690 --> 22:05.620
Has Yan Heng...

22:05.620 --> 22:06.580
talked to you about that?

22:09.590 --> 22:10.420
Yes.

22:11.250 --> 22:12.050
That's good.

22:17.180 --> 22:18.050
Uncle,

22:18.570 --> 22:21.290
when will Yan Heng return to China?

22:23.510 --> 22:24.580
He's not abroad.

22:24.600 --> 22:25.440
He's at home.

22:57.940 --> 22:59.790
He's been in Hang City.

23:01.940 --> 23:04.180
Why won't he even meet me once?

23:07.340 --> 23:09.260
We were together for seven years.

23:10.570 --> 23:13.810
Don't I even deserve a proper goodbye?

23:15.460 --> 23:17.330
Am I that annoying?

23:18.970 --> 23:21.140
What did I do wrong?

24:00.570 --> 24:01.490
If you have time,

24:01.520 --> 24:03.760
try visiting places with lots of trees.

24:04.140 --> 24:05.420
The energy of plants

24:05.450 --> 24:06.580
can soothe your body and mind.

24:07.310 --> 24:09.460
Places with lots of plants have plenty of oxygen,

24:09.640 --> 24:11.290
which can help ease your mood.

25:49.460 --> 25:52.110
Maybe drinking two more bags will help me fall asleep.

26:04.380 --> 26:07.340
It's okay. As long as I can fall asleep, it'll be okay.

26:08.340 --> 26:10.170
It'll be fine once I'm asleep.

26:28.640 --> 26:33.780
[The closing day of the JIC Summit in Hang City]

26:35.050 --> 26:36.290
Yan Heng hasn't come, right?

26:37.290 --> 26:37.820
No.

26:38.210 --> 26:39.860
The summit's over and he still hasn't shown up.

26:40.470 --> 26:41.630
He's definitely not coming.

26:44.730 --> 26:46.100
From what I know about men like him,

26:46.100 --> 26:47.250
he doesn't have the guts to come.

26:47.250 --> 26:48.250
If he dares to come, I'll...

26:48.250 --> 26:48.940
Alright.

26:49.640 --> 26:50.480
Keep it down.

26:50.500 --> 26:51.870
There are guests around.

27:00.770 --> 27:03.140
You said you need an invoice, right?

27:03.420 --> 27:03.900
Yes.

27:05.140 --> 27:06.340
I'll send it to you right away.

27:06.340 --> 27:07.010
Okay.

27:23.170 --> 27:29.610
♫The moment I see you, all my worries turn transparent♫

27:30.300 --> 27:37.710
♫In the silence, the sound of my heartbeat grows clearer♫

27:37.730 --> 27:43.130
♫The entire world reflects in your eyes♫

27:43.280 --> 27:51.780
♫Make a wish, can the snow fall slowly?♫

27:51.380 --> 27:53.420
I wonder how long this meeting will last.

27:52.380 --> 27:55.890
♫Even if we're destined to meet and miss each other♫

27:56.130 --> 28:02.030
♫Life is finally complete♫

28:02.560 --> 28:06.030
♫Watching the snow fall, flake by flake♫

28:06.050 --> 28:09.530
♫Slowly melting away my thoughts♫

28:09.560 --> 28:13.010
♫Smiling, I wave goodbye as you head home♫

28:13.190 --> 28:16.770
♫But I never said those words♫

28:16.800 --> 28:20.320
♫Watching the snow fall, flake by flake♫

28:20.420 --> 28:24.240
♫When will love bloom into a flower?♫

28:24.260 --> 28:29.960
♫You wander the world, forgetting to reply♫

28:30.140 --> 28:33.730
♫When you turn around, I'll be right there♫

29:03.010 --> 29:03.970
Hello, Xiangya.

29:04.900 --> 29:06.420
Hello, what are you doing?

29:07.770 --> 29:09.210
I'm tidying up the room.

29:09.420 --> 29:11.970
I'm putting away things related to Yan Heng.

29:12.340 --> 29:13.420
But...

29:13.940 --> 29:16.420
I haven't figured out how to tell my parents yet.

29:17.520 --> 29:19.760
Anyway, that guy isn't often in China.

29:19.820 --> 29:21.380
Your parents probably wouldn't think of him.

29:22.420 --> 29:23.730
I'm an adult after all.

29:24.050 --> 29:25.900
I don't want them to always worry about me.

29:27.300 --> 29:29.900
I still want to handle it myself before telling them.

29:30.730 --> 29:32.450
I don't want to keep it from them for too long either.

29:33.580 --> 29:35.730
Don't put too much pressure on yourself.

29:36.670 --> 29:38.800
Take a day off tomorrow and rest at home.

29:39.770 --> 29:41.450
Don't think too much. I'm hanging up.

29:55.960 --> 29:57.600
I've finished all the medicine.

30:18.290 --> 30:18.900
No big deal.

30:20.530 --> 30:22.940
Hello, I'd like to make an appointment with Dr. He Suye.

30:24.070 --> 30:25.550
You're Miss Shen, right?

30:25.570 --> 30:26.480
Yes.

30:26.530 --> 30:27.040
Dr. He

30:27.060 --> 30:28.140
is not here today.

30:28.420 --> 30:29.970
He only works here on Saturdays.

30:30.320 --> 30:32.110
Usually, he works at the TCM hospital.

30:32.450 --> 30:33.180
The TCM hospital?

30:33.180 --> 30:33.690
Yes.

30:35.060 --> 30:36.930
Do you want me to make an appointment with another doctor for you?

30:37.210 --> 30:38.290
No.

30:38.290 --> 30:38.820
Thank you.

30:38.820 --> 30:39.450
Okay.

30:46.530 --> 30:48.450
Okay, make sure to get enough rest.

30:48.450 --> 30:49.970
Let me know if you have any problems.

30:50.250 --> 30:51.100
Okay, thank you, doctor.

30:58.350 --> 30:59.980
Why are you using my pen again?

31:02.490 --> 31:03.450
You guys

31:03.450 --> 31:05.210
organize today's ward round records later.

31:06.010 --> 31:06.490
Also,

31:06.730 --> 31:07.530
how's the osteosarcoma report

31:07.530 --> 31:09.050
you two have been working on?

31:09.340 --> 31:09.970
It's done,

31:10.250 --> 31:11.820
but we still need to cross-check

31:11.820 --> 31:13.180
some data and conclusions.

31:13.660 --> 31:15.450
Okay. I can help you review it later.

31:15.450 --> 31:16.820
Okay, thank you, Senior He.

31:17.050 --> 31:18.010
Senior He,

31:18.180 --> 31:19.620
I've finished my thesis too.

31:19.690 --> 31:20.820
Can you also help me...

31:20.840 --> 31:21.910
Sure, no problem.

31:23.550 --> 31:24.670
You've all finished?

31:23.790 --> 31:29.490
[So I want to ask if I can go to the TCM hospital.]

31:23.790 --> 31:29.490
[Hello, Dr. He. I went for my follow-up visit, but I heard from the clinic that you're in the TCM hospital today.]

31:25.660 --> 31:26.680
I'm the only one who hasn't finished?

31:33.620 --> 31:34.660
Aren't you ashamed?

31:35.290 --> 31:36.050
How about this?

31:36.530 --> 31:37.690
When Li Jie finishes his thesis,

31:37.690 --> 31:39.010
I'll review both of yours together.

31:39.490 --> 31:41.210
I might not have time after reviewing their report today.

31:41.770 --> 31:42.490
Okay.

31:45.380 --> 31:46.420
Why haven't you finished it yet?

31:47.580 --> 31:48.620
I'm working on it.

31:49.050 --> 31:49.820
I can't believe you.

31:51.120 --> 31:52.910
You're free today?

31:55.110 --> 31:56.800
Yes, I'm having a day off today.

31:59.210 --> 31:59.930
Then come.

32:03.490 --> 32:05.010
Li Jie is careless.

32:05.780 --> 32:06.890
Gu Ping, Qiu Tian,

32:07.230 --> 32:08.380
take your theses with you later

32:08.380 --> 32:09.580
and wait for me in the break room.

32:09.580 --> 32:10.580
I have something to do.

32:10.900 --> 32:11.140
Okay.

32:11.140 --> 32:11.820
Okay, Senior.

32:12.940 --> 32:13.420
Bye bye.

32:14.010 --> 32:14.490
Bye bye.

33:05.830 --> 33:06.590
Shen Xifan.

33:45.620 --> 33:46.530
What's wrong?

33:48.210 --> 33:49.530
I'm...

33:50.210 --> 33:51.650
a bit haggard today.

33:52.010 --> 33:53.490
You're getting better, right?

33:53.600 --> 33:54.490
It's okay.

34:00.580 --> 34:03.620
Actually, you don't need to give me special treatment.

34:03.970 --> 34:05.900
I can just go to the outpatient clinic and register.

34:06.210 --> 34:07.620
I'm not giving you special treatment.

34:08.080 --> 34:09.650
I'm not a doctor in the TCM department.

34:09.679 --> 34:10.989
So you can't get an appointment with me in the outpatient clinic.

34:12.550 --> 34:14.719
You... are not a TCM physician?

34:14.820 --> 34:15.820
I am a TCM physician,

34:15.820 --> 34:17.380
but I'm in the TCM oncology department.

34:19.219 --> 34:20.739
Those who make appointments with me

34:21.010 --> 34:23.050
are usually cancer patients.

34:27.940 --> 34:30.090
I was worried the atmosphere in the oncology department might scare you,

34:30.300 --> 34:31.090
so...

34:31.090 --> 34:32.690
I arranged to meet you here instead.

34:40.610 --> 34:41.050
Alright,

34:41.170 --> 34:41.860
don't just stand here.

34:42.110 --> 34:42.949
Go sit over there for a while.

34:43.570 --> 34:44.130
Okay.

34:47.389 --> 34:48.949
Why did you come for a follow-up visit so soon?

34:49.090 --> 34:51.170
Didn't I just prescribe more medicine for you last Saturday?

34:53.650 --> 34:55.090
I've finished all the medicine.

34:56.170 --> 34:57.220
You've finished it all?

34:58.740 --> 34:59.650
It's only been four days.

34:59.650 --> 35:01.090
You finished a week's worth of medicine within four days?

35:02.570 --> 35:04.420
I really couldn't fall sleep,

35:04.420 --> 35:06.130
so I drank a bit more.

35:07.780 --> 35:09.050
Even medicine has its toxicity.

35:09.260 --> 35:11.170
Even though it's herbal medicine, you can't drink it like that.

35:14.300 --> 35:15.130
Dr. He,

35:15.950 --> 35:18.320
are all these plants medicinal herbs?

35:21.340 --> 35:21.860
Those

35:22.280 --> 35:23.030
are perilla leaves.

35:24.360 --> 35:25.720
Perilla leaves?

35:26.900 --> 35:28.010
Isn't that your name?

35:29.890 --> 35:31.490
Perilla leaves might seem unremarkable,

35:31.510 --> 35:33.280
but they're widely distributed and used.

35:33.450 --> 35:34.170
For example,

35:34.450 --> 35:35.530
you can wrap grilled meat with them.

35:40.000 --> 35:40.920
Have a seat over there.

35:40.950 --> 35:41.760
I'll take your pulse.

35:42.290 --> 35:42.960
Okay.

35:49.050 --> 35:49.740
Sit down.

35:50.170 --> 35:50.860
Thank you.

35:55.880 --> 35:57.690
Come on, let me take your pulse.

36:10.510 --> 36:11.390
Don't move.

36:12.350 --> 36:13.900
Keep your hand still while I'm taking your pulse.

36:39.490 --> 36:40.700
How have you been lately?

36:42.050 --> 36:42.700
How about your sleep

36:43.240 --> 36:43.760
and mood?

36:46.920 --> 36:47.850
Everything's been fine.

36:48.490 --> 36:49.530
It's just that

36:50.010 --> 36:51.940
I've been quite busy with work recently,

36:52.050 --> 36:54.740
so I've been sleeping late and unable to get enough sleep.

36:55.220 --> 36:55.820
But...

36:56.370 --> 36:57.260
the quality of sleep is okay.

37:06.370 --> 37:09.000
Maybe you should get a new doctor.

37:10.840 --> 37:11.910
My medical skills aren't that great.

37:17.980 --> 37:19.190
Dr. He,

37:20.090 --> 37:22.660
last time you mentioned dietary restrictions.

37:23.790 --> 37:25.900
And now you're giving up on me?

37:26.230 --> 37:27.310
I didn't say that.

37:29.580 --> 37:30.820
Your words sound like

37:31.450 --> 37:32.940
I have no medical ethics.

37:37.160 --> 37:37.910
Another hand.

37:40.300 --> 37:41.010
I need to take your pulse.

37:50.670 --> 37:52.090
Besides insomnia,

37:52.700 --> 37:54.450
can you help with something else?

37:55.170 --> 37:56.300
My mom said

37:56.460 --> 37:57.790
I've been looking pale

37:58.330 --> 37:59.480
and lacking energy lately.

38:01.720 --> 38:02.720
Of course.

38:03.270 --> 38:04.020
But...

38:04.340 --> 38:05.610
sleep is still the most important thing.

38:06.350 --> 38:07.460
If you can't sleep well,

38:07.480 --> 38:08.850
how can your body recover?

38:08.880 --> 38:09.630
Right?

38:11.750 --> 38:12.460
I...

38:14.000 --> 38:15.890
It's not that I don't want to sleep.

38:32.370 --> 38:33.090
Alright then.

38:33.860 --> 38:34.540
Well,

38:34.560 --> 38:35.810
I guess my medical skills are indeed not good enough.

38:42.760 --> 38:43.910
I'll write you a prescription.

39:37.050 --> 39:37.740
Done.

39:38.900 --> 39:41.090
Take this prescription to the clinic and have them decoct the medicine.

39:41.130 --> 39:42.090
If there are any issues,

39:42.090 --> 39:43.610
tell them to call me directly.

39:44.000 --> 39:44.850
Okay.

39:44.880 --> 39:45.470
Thank you.

39:46.180 --> 39:47.820
Remember, you must avoid certain foods.

39:47.840 --> 39:49.030
No cold drinks.

39:49.720 --> 39:51.110
If you really don't want to drink anything hot,

39:51.140 --> 39:52.710
at least have it at room temperature.

39:53.290 --> 39:54.250
How about...

39:54.650 --> 39:55.420
no ice?

39:58.190 --> 39:59.460
Drink whatever you want.

39:59.820 --> 40:01.490
You're not exactly an obedient patient anyway.

40:02.230 --> 40:03.750
If you want cold drinks, go ahead.

40:03.890 --> 40:05.290
Maybe even eat two tubs of ice cream while you're at it.

40:05.420 --> 40:07.020
That'll surely cure all your ailments.

40:08.080 --> 40:09.600
You're a doctor.

40:09.850 --> 40:11.650
Why are you mad at a patient?

40:13.400 --> 40:14.080
Am I?

40:14.120 --> 40:15.030
Yes, you are.

40:16.170 --> 40:17.000
Fine, if you say so.

40:22.970 --> 40:24.620
Well then, Dr. He,

40:25.220 --> 40:26.930
I'll let you get back to work. I'm leaving.

40:36.490 --> 40:37.140
Right,

40:39.050 --> 40:40.450
thank you for sparing time to see me.

40:43.820 --> 40:44.700
See you on Saturday.

40:46.620 --> 40:47.340
See you on Saturday.
